_sText:
General Info:
dm_castle_invasion took about 8 hours to create, texture, light, etc.. Making it the map I put the most time into. Also is the first map I've made with a 3d skybox.

Features:
.nav file for bots
3d skybox
Plenty of open space for movement, also enclosed areas for ambushes

Expectations:
I haven't tested the gameplay any, so far it's just been created. Leave feedback on how gameplay is and any problems that occur.
